parameters: 初期スタート・ルイリセット用
プレイヤーのライト設定
A creepy monster is persistently slamming the bed.

\n<Monster>...Oh, my apologies. I didn't notice you since
we've never had a guest before.

\n<Monster>By the way, what are those dangerous things you're
holding in both hands? Are you some kind of thief?
\n<Rui>...You talk quite fluently. It makes this awkward.

\n<Rui>I'm not intending to be a thief... but depending
on you, it might end up the same.

\n<Rui>You, and the other monsters like you. Do you have
the key to this world?

\n<Monster>The two despairs, right? That information crossed
my mind a little while ago. It was a very
unpleasant feeling.
\n<Rui>So the other two creatures have the key?

\n<Monster>I could tell you... but first, could you put down
those dangerous things in your hands?

\n<Monster>From my perspective, you are a thief. I'm not so
naive as to listen to a thief with weapons.

\n<Rui>You're not wrong, but that doesn't mean I can
afford to show any vulnerability.

\n<Rui>Mari and Damaki. Names I heard in the world of
snow.

\n<Rui>Are they trying to make me kill... targets of
revenge, my family?

\n<Rui>No, the Eye itself said it didn't know about this
door's world...

\n<Rui>Either way, if I keep going like this... I'll
become a murderer...

\n<Rui>But then again... I'm not such a good person as to
sacrifice my own body...

\n<Rui>Even so, that monster was calling out human
names...

\n<Rui>...Next time, I won't let them escape. That's all
there is to it.
\n<Monster>Not yet. Please put your arms behind your back.

\n<Monster>From my perspective, you are still a threat. You
understand, don't you?
I can't ask any more than this
\n<Rui>I have a bad feeling about this...

\n<Rui>You're not wrong, but that doesn't mean I can
afford to show any vulnerability.

\n<Rui>Mari and Damaki. Names I heard in the world of
snow.

\n<Rui>Are they trying to make me kill... my family... my
targets of revenge?

\n<Rui>No. The Eye itself said it didn't know about the
world beyond this door...

\n<Rui>Either way, if I keep going like this... I'll
become a murderer...

\n<Rui>But that doesn't mean... I'm such a good person
that I'd sacrifice my own body...
\n<Rui>But still, that monster was calling human names...
\n<Rui>...No point in thinking about it now.

\n<Rui>...Next time, I won't let them escape. That's all
there is to it.

Rui, who felt averse to killing a monster that
spoke fluently, was caught off guard.

The monster covered her face, her vision was
blocked, and she couldn't breathe.

If she had quickly readjusted her grip on the
sword, she might have managed...

Rui, who had fallen into a panic, was unable to
make that decision.

And of course, prey that forgets to fight back in
confusion is just waiting to be hunted.
\n<Rui>"I won't be fooled by your act anymore."

\n<Rui>"Marie and Damaki... Names I heard in the world of
snow."

\n<Rui>"Are they trying to make me kill... my own family,
my targets for revenge?"

\n<Rui>"No, the Eye itself said it didn't know about the
world beyond this door..."

\n<Rui>"Either way, if I keep going like this... I'll
become a murderer..."

\n<Rui>"But that doesn't mean... I'm such a good person
that I'd sacrifice my own body..."

\n<Rui>"Even so, that monster was calling out human
names..."
\n<Rui>"No point in thinking about it now."

\n<Rui>"...Next time, I definitely won't let them escape.
That's all there is to it."
